preference.name: ItemRevision_group_order
preference.preference_description: Specifies the order by types of children components to be displayed when expanding the node of objects of type "ItemRevision" in the "My Teamcenter" perspective of the rich client. Other children components whose types are not in the list will be displayed after the children components whose types are specified here. The valid values are Business Object type name. If this preference is not configured, then the children components will be displayed based on ItemRevision_DefaultChildProperties preference values.
